{
  "stem": "27509.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was always the youngest in any situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Never looked for friends of my own age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I always looked for people older than I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I fitted in very, very comfortably.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I felt at home among older people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The-- the more serious the situation was, the more at home I felt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At school, they used to call me [POLISH], the walking seriousness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only in terms of-- of general-- of general self-awareness, rather than-- than-- than an outgoing act.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you used to go to the-- to the taxation of his-- which, of course, a government instrumentality, and-- and we were the taxpayers and the supplicants.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were at the wrong end of the stick in the situation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I can't say that I have personally-- excuse me-- encountered this sort of thing until, of course, until my student days in Warsaw because-- and that may be appropriate to mention at this stage because you are asking me explicitly about anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Being a student at the university level, we were entitled to be-- to be serving in the officers corps-- the cadet corp, officers corp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were duty-bound by law to-- to offer ourselves for selection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we presented ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And contrary to all normal procedure, when everybody was trying to get out of things in the army and so on, so forth, all the questions we answered was in the positive.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Are you well?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are you healthy?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you have any disabilities?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- everything was answered positively because we knew beforehand that we, as Jews, we would never be accepted into the officers corps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we always got a number above the norm and sent home free without any commitment.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
